---
title: Carb Smart Paneer and Spinach with Roasted Cauliflower
description: This low-starch supper is inspired by the Indian takeout classic, palak paneer! Hearty paneer and wholesome spinach marry in this aromatic curry. In place of the rice, the curry is paired with a bed of roasted cauliflower!
